### Checkbox composition

Checkbox is composed of a fixed-size Control box and an optional Text content zone (Label + Helper text). The control and text zones are laid out by the inner Content frame. hasLabel toggles the entire Text content zone; hasHelperText toggles the Helper text row within it.

