| Label | – | Primary label text; rendered when hasLabel=True |
| └ textStyle | Body/M | Gotham Book 16/26. Fills the text zone width and wraps to multiple lines |
| Helper text | – | Supporting copy beneath the label; rendered when hasHelperText=true. Carries the error guidance in the Error state |
